        6: quadratic temperature term coefficient
        7: linear interaction term coefficient (strain * temp)
        8: quadratic interaction term coefficient ((strain^2) * temp)
        9: logistic/hyperbolic tangent saturation steepness parameter
       10: logistic/hyperbolic tangent saturation amplitude parameter
       11: asymmetry/yield behavior coefficient (sign(strain))
