            p[6]: cubic strain coefficient
            p[7]: exponential decay rate for temp effect on stiffness (positive)
            p[8]: quadratic strain * linear temp interaction
            p[9]: linear strain * quadratic temp interaction
            p[10]: inverse temperature coefficient (softening)
