    Parameters:
    - params: array-like coefficients [p0,...p11]

    Model form:
        σ = 
          + p0                                    # constant offset stress (e.g. residual stress)
          + p1 * ε * exp(-p2 * T)                 # thermal softening linear term
          + p3 * ε^2                              # quadratic hardening
          + p4 * ε^3                              # cubic hardening
          + p5 * T                               # linear temperature effect
          + p6 * T^2                             # quadratic temperature effect
          + p7 * ε * T                           # linear interaction term
          + p8 * ε^2 * T                         # quadratic-strain & linear-temp interaction
          + tanh_saturation                      # smooth saturation via tanh on |ε|
          + asymmetry_term                       # asymmetry/yield behavior with power-law exponent
          + p11 * log(1+max(ε,0))               # logarithmic microstructure effect on positive strains

    Saturation term:
        tanh_saturation = p9 * tanh(p10 * |ε|)

    Asymmetry term:
        asymmetry_term = sign(ε) * |ε|^{power}
